contentrichtext.text: '''QOS''', '''QoS''', or '''Qos''' could refer to one of several things: * [[Quality of service]] in computer network trafficking refers to resource reservation control mechanisms * ''Quantum of Solace'', works related to Ian Fleming's James Bond: ** The original [[For_Your_Eyes_Only_(short_story_collection)#Quantum_of_Solace|short story]] ** [[Quantum of Solace|A 2008 cinematic production]] with a plot written by Michael G. Wilson * [[Quarterdeck Office Systems]], a software company that is now part of Symantec * [[Queen of the South F.C.]], a professional association football club formed and in existence since 1919 in Dumfries, Scotland, often colloquially abbreviated to ''QoS'' (as listed on the club badge) * [[Queensland Ornithological Society Inc|Queensland Ornithological Society]], a state birding organisation in Australia * The Edomite god [[Kaus]] *[[A Question of Sport]], television sports quiz show. {{disambiguation}}
